PrecisAmendment to the NATIONAL PARKS WILDLIFE REGULATIONS revising the section of the regulations which specifies the open season dates for Eider and Oldsquaw duck hunting in Mingan Archipelago National Park Reserve in Quebec, by making reference to the schedule of dates listed in the Migratory Birds Regulations.
